Basic Rules  ("<rulesets/exceptions.xml>")
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* CatchThrowable Rule
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

  Checks for catching a <<<Throwable>>>. In most cases that is much too broad, and is also dangerous
  because it can catch exceptions such as <<<ThreadDeath>>> and <<<OutOfMemoryError>>>.

